{"tid":1049033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：錯字唔知 掛起唔發覺  民建聯盲撐「開日大嶼」 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-03-06T04:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T12:58:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"619e8451a0f7b2e8a11d13c3b2c2afb9e83b0a59","tid":1049033,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190306/20626947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F20626947&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=c8446134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F20626947&h=799114e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190306/20626947</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：錯字唔知 掛起唔發覺 <br />\n民建聯盲撐「開日大嶼」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190306/large/a1104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190306%2Flarge%2Fa1104a.gif&h=3b816b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工黨趙恩來影低民建聯落力撐「開日大嶼」嘅相放上網。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n被指要動用一萬億元嘅填海工程「明日大嶼」，建制派梗係要全力撐啦，不過撐都唔可以撐得咁肉酸，否則就會變豬隊友，為特首林鄭月娥幫倒忙，八方講緊邊個？咪就係成日越幫越忙嘅民建聯囉！噚日嘅嘅荃灣區議會特別會議，由民建聯陳恒鑌動議撐明日大嶼，會前佢哋動員自己友去請願，當然要大堆頭影張相交功課俾人睇。成隊人喺場外拉出兩條「儘快展開『開日大嶼』相關研究」嘅橫額。乜鬼嘢嚟㗎？乜唔係撐「明日大嶼」咩？點解變「開日大嶼」？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190306/large/1551802738_5b94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190306%2Flarge%2F1551802738_5b94.jpg&h=1064e6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「保皇黨都係文盲」<br />\n<br />\n不過最豬嘅並唔係將明日大嶼變開日大嶼，而係民建聯攤開咗橫額都仲未知衰，掛埋出嚟都唔覺有錯嗰下好嘢。其實，錯其他字都還可以，「明日大嶼」幾粒字都可以寫錯，究竟係咪真心撐嘅先？<br />\n<br />\n喺現場嘅工黨趙恩來、夏希諾同埋民主黨盧俊宇就影埋相公告天下，佢哋都不禁大嘆「保皇黨都係文盲，咩叫『開日大嶼』？」、「民建聯帶錯橫額去示威？！」、「原來除咗『明日大嶼』計劃，還有『開日大嶼』計劃！」 聽聞民建聯為咗搞呢個動議，用咗條荃灣區議會從來冇用過嘅會議常規，開呢個特別大會，前後不足十個工作天通知期。咁心急，難怪字都寫錯啦！<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：《流浪地球》撐唔起 周日旺角零票房 (李八方)"},{"pid":"1dafcd0f1029a1f33261c02569759092449875b9","tid":1049033,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"講錯埋口號就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802d220533889fbd64f29f148d566b9c0c319ca2","tid":1049033,"uid":14737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dafcd0f1029a1f33261c02569759092449875b9","tid":1049033,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"講錯埋口號就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"過去同d阿伯講, 個計劃叫開日大嶼, 唔信你睇下塊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地應該真係連口號都會叫錯"},{"pid":"14326d6a61dd5aac0d1411918fdbbbb8b76679f7","tid":1049033,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802d220533889fbd64f29f148d566b9c0c319ca2","tid":1049033,"uid":14737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dafcd0f1029a1f33261c02569759092449875b9","tid":1049033,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"講錯埋口號就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"過去同d阿伯講, 個計劃叫開日大嶼, 唔信你睇下塊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地應該真係連口號都會叫錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"之後有線記者訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}